&lt;DIV&gt;No December updates.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Dec 2005 01:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
      <author>Kytherea</author>
      <guid>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=shamanbalance&amp;message.id=6079#M6079</guid>
      <dc:creator>Kytherea</dc:creator>
